yle="padding-right: 0 ; text-align: right ;  vertical-align: middle; vertical-align: middle ; vertical-align: bottom ; ">&nbsp;</td><td style="padding-left: 0 ; padding-right: 0 ; text-align: right ;  vertical-align: middle; vertical-align: middle ; vertical-align: bottom ; ">(335</td><td style="padding-left: 0 ; text-align: left ;  vertical-align: middle; vertical-align: middle ; vertical-align: bottom ; ">)</td></tr><tr><td style="vertical-align: bottom ; ">Tax impact of unrealized (gain) loss on derivative asset</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-right: 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom="">&nbsp;</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-left: 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom="">—</td><td style="vertical-align: bottom ; ">&nbsp;</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-right: 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom="">&nbsp;</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-left: 0px; padding-right: 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom="">(90</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-left: 0px; text-align: left; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader-inline-border-bottom="">)</td><td style="vertical-align: bottom ; ">&nbsp;</td><td style="border-bottom: 1pt solid black; padding-right: 0px; text-align: right; vertical-align: bottom; --darkreader-inline-border-bottom: var(--darkreader-border-000000, #8c8273);" data-darkreader